atlantic county library system is the county library system of atlantic county, new jersey. the library system is the information center in atlantic county. the library system includes ten branch libraries located throughout atlantic county: brigantine, egg harbor city, egg harbor township, galloway township, hammonton, longport, mays landing, pleasantville, somers point, and ventnor. the computerized public access catalog contains over 500,000 books, audio-visual and downloadable items. atlantic county library system also has a bookmobile, books-by-mail, and other outreach services.